    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 <strong>夜市模拟器：打造并扩展你自己的夜市！</strong> 🌙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好体验真实的夜市生活了吗？</strong><br>《夜市模拟器》是一款细致有趣的模拟经营游戏。你将建立并扩展自己的市场，在进货与销售之间做出策略决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/3b9a5dc3af2bc5ef999a0d371ced4a5a.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/3b9a5dc3af2bc5ef999a0d371ced4a5a.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/3b9a5dc3af2bc5ef999a0d371ced4a5a.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开设商店、摆放商品、满足顾客需求，解锁商品许可证，雇佣员工、管理团队，壮大你的夜市帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📘 <strong>关于本游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《夜市模拟器》是一款沉浸式商业模拟游戏，让玩家打造、管理并发展属于自己的夜市。<br>围绕买卖机制，制定价格策略、满足客户需求，扩大市场规模！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>许可证系统：</strong><br>销售商品、提升等级、解锁新产品。每张许可证意味着更多商品与更高利润！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/b9dbde839a3994e0378e6ee45bb10fda.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/b9dbde839a3994e0378e6ee45bb10fda.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/b9dbde839a3994e0378e6ee45bb10fda.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>仓库与库存管理：</strong><br>接收箱装商品，搬运入库，储备库存并及时补货，打造高效管理流程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/44996e835d01ebcc64aaa1b83d4403d9.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/44996e835d01ebcc64aaa1b83d4403d9.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/44996e835d01ebcc64aaa1b83d4403d9.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>员工管理：</strong><br>雇佣收银员、搬运工、补货员等员工。提升自动化效率，节省宝贵时间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/1aff5627baf11bc3b91a2713c364e3cd.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/1aff5627baf11bc3b91a2713c364e3cd.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/1aff5627baf11bc3b91a2713c364e3cd.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>可扩展的商店：</strong><br>用赚来的资金扩展商铺、解锁新区域、陈列更多商品。店面越大，客流越多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/73a042aecc3dd0033f275f5552bf4ab4.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/73a042aecc3dd0033f275f5552bf4ab4.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/73a042aecc3dd0033f275f5552bf4ab4.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>多样化货架类型：</strong><br>使用冷冻柜、冰箱、普通货架、水果摊等方式科学陈列商品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/94ed513a357289f205ca1f7af7a96b20.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/94ed513a357289f205ca1f7af7a96b20.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/94ed513a357289f205ca1f7af7a96b20.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>动态定价与盈亏分析：</strong><br>自由定价、调整利润率，用聪明的策略优化你的运营！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/eb464cdf5398194c5bb4666b82fa9506.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/eb464cdf5398194c5bb4666b82fa9506.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/eb464cdf5398194c5bb4666b82fa9506.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>商店自定义：</strong><br>给你的商店命名，自定义外观风格，展现独一无二的品牌形象！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/52a9192124521dda43cf125301d0d557.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/52a9192124521dda43cf125301d0d557.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/52a9192124521dda43cf125301d0d557.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>游戏模式与内容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>自由模式：</strong><br>按照自己的节奏游玩，自由发展业务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>任务与目标：</strong><br>完成特定任务赢取奖励，按照引导逐步成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 <strong>社区与开发</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《夜市模拟器》是一款随着玩家反馈不断更新完善的游戏。<br>每次更新都会带来新内容、系统优化和基于玩家建议的新功能。<br><strong>你的建议对我们非常重要！</strong></p>",
